項之未遂犯罰之。","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/CHDM/110%2c%e8%a8%b4%2c840%2c20220831%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"CHDM,110,訴,840,20220831,1","JYEAR":"110","JCASE":"訴","JNO":"840","JDATE":"20220831","JTITLE":"準強盜等"}